msgctxt "sn48.28:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.28:0.2"
msgid "3. Chaḷindriyavagga "
msgstr "3. The Six Faculties "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 28. Sambuddhasutta → buddhasuttaṃ (bj) | arahatā 2 or buddho (pts1)
msgctxt "sn48.28:0.3"
msgid "28. Sambuddhasutta "
msgstr "28. Awakened "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.206, sc1
msgctxt "sn48.28:1.1"
msgid "“Chayimāni, bhikkhave, indriyāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these six faculties. "

msgctxt "sn48.28:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cha? "
msgstr "What six? "

msgctxt "sn48.28:1.3"
msgid "Cakkhundriyaṃ, sotindriyaṃ, ghānindriyaṃ, jivhindriyaṃ, kāyindriyaṃ, manindriyaṃ. "
msgstr "The faculties of the eye, ear, nose, tongue, body, and mind. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.28:1.4"
msgid "Yāvakīvañcāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imesaṃ channaṃ indriyānaṃ samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ nābbhaññāsiṃ, neva tāvāhaṃ, bhikkhave, sadevake loke samārake sabrahmake sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiyā pajāya sadevamanussāya ‘anuttaraṃ sammāsambodhiṃ abhisambuddho’ti paccaññāsiṃ. "
msgstr "As long as I didn’t truly understand these six faculties’ gratification, drawback, and escape for what they are, I didn’t announce my supreme perfect awakening in this world with its gods, Māras, and Brahmās, this population with its ascetics and brahmins, its gods and humans. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.28:1.5"
msgid "Yato ca khvāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imesaṃ channaṃ indriyānaṃ samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ abbhaññāsiṃ, athāhaṃ, bhikkhave, sadevake loke samārake sabrahmake sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiyā pajāya sadevamanussāya ‘anuttaraṃ sammāsambodhiṃ abhisambuddho’ti paccaññāsiṃ. "
msgstr "But when I did truly understand these six faculties’ gratification, drawback, and escape for what they are, I announced my supreme perfect awakening in this world with its gods, Māras, and Brahmās, this population with its ascetics and brahmins, its gods and humans. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.28:1.6"
msgid "Ñāṇañca pana me dassanaṃ udapādi: "
msgstr "Knowledge and vision arose in me: "

msgctxt "sn48.28:1.7"
msgid "‘akuppā me vimutti, ayamantimā jāti, natthi dāni punabbhavo’”ti. "
msgstr "‘My freedom is unshakable; this is my last rebirth; now there are no more future lives.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.28:1.8"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

